      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "小李后来学乖了，开始用肉眼判断趋势。",
        "他看到一只股票连续涨了五天，觉得是上涨趋势，于是买入。",
        "结果第六天价格突然掉头向下——原来那只是震荡市中的一次随机波动。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s013",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "肉眼不可靠。",
        "我们需要一个数学工具来客观判断趋势。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "simple_linear_regression"
      ],
      "id": "s014",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "simple_linear_regression"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "一个最直接的工具：<term id=\"simple_linear_regression\">简单线性回归</term>。",
        "它试图在价格和时间之间画一条直线。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s015",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "直线的斜率，就是趋势的方向和强度。",
        "斜率正 → 上涨；斜率负 → 下跌。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "dependent_variable",
        "independent_variable"
      ],
      "id": "s016",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "dependent_variable",
        "independent_variable"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "模型里有两个关键角色：",
        "<term id=\"dependent_variable\">因变量</term>（你想预测的，比如价格）和<term id=\"independent_variable\">自变量</term>（用来预测的，比如时间）。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "Y = \\beta_0 + \\beta_1 X + \\epsilon",
        "spoken": "Y等于beta_0加beta_1乘X再加epsilon"
      },
      "id": "s017",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "数学形式很简单：",
        "价格 = 截距 + 斜率 × 时间 + 误差"
      ],
      "type": "formula"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "residual"
      ],
      "id": "s018",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "residual"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "模型预测值和实际值之间的差距，叫<term id=\"residual\">残差</term>。",
        "残差越小，模型拟合得越好。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "r_squared"
      ],
      "id": "s019",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "r_squared"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "衡量拟合好坏的常用指标是<term id=\"r_squared\">R²</term>。",
        "R²越接近1，说明模型解释力越强。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
